{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ea2f2a62bd","title":"陈伯达接见天津赴京汇报代表团时的讲话摘要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"448c0fcb2d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":22,"articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"公安与法律","id":"53b954d860","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b07f3c2ef0","type":"title","text":"陈伯达接见天津赴京汇报代表团时的讲话摘要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"360bb6c4f3","type":"paragraph","text":"都是老话、好话，可以重复地讲。我准备说的都是好话。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e76c5f828","type":"paragraph","text":"1．我们还是主张贯彻执行毛主席按系统搞大联合的指示，不赞成跨行业的组织，包括大联筹反复辟，这就可能得罪你们了，你们要打就打。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"126dffe364","type":"paragraph","text":"2．要把参加“大联筹”的群众同头头区别开来，“大联筹”有些头头搞了很多坏事，亲者痛，仇者快。他们做的坏事是不能容忍的。对一些头头做的坏事，参加大联筹的群众不能替他负责任。这就没有压力了嘛！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcd9bc278b","type":"paragraph","text":"3．遵照毛主席关于多作自我批评，少批评别人的指示，继续协商，能快一点成功是好的，对抓革命、促生产有利。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"491bcd0131","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志批评了《政法公社》。他指出：","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34a9bcbd93","type":"paragraph","text":"北京政法学院《政法公社》，这个学校里一小批学生组织《政法公社》要在全国夺权，他们到天津帮助万、张反党集团夺公安局的权，在小站帮助张凤琴夺王凤春的权。群众是最后的裁判者。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ea2f2a62bd","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}